and it turned out to be nothing.

8
00:00:29,279 --> 00:00:31,698
Let's hope there's no
abnormalities this year.

9
00:00:31,781 --> 00:00:33,074
Right.

10
00:00:33,908 --> 00:00:36,911
<i>My love life is abnormal enough.</i>

11
00:00:38,246 --> 00:00:40,540
He keeps his nose like…

12
00:00:41,875 --> 00:00:44,961
<i>It was so fun being together.</i>

13
00:00:46,212 --> 00:00:49,632
<i>But because I made</i>
<i>a move on him too quickly…</i>

14
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:51,760
Kagiya?

15
00:00:51,843 --> 00:00:53,303
I'm sorry.

16
00:00:53,386 --> 00:00:55,305
Wait, Kagiya!

17
00:00:56,139 --> 00:00:58,058
<i>Because I was too aggressive,</i>

18
00:00:59,809 --> 00:01:01,561
